## Project Mental Model

```txt
User
  |
  v
Frontend React/Vite
  |
  v
Backend Express
  |
  +-> MongoDB stores users/chats/messages/sources
  +-> Search API finds web results
  +-> Scraper extracts readable source content
  +-> LLM generates cited answer
  +-> SSE streams answer tokens to frontend
```

## Core Product Loop

```txt
query
  -> search
  -> scrape
  -> prepare numbered sources
  -> generate AI answer
  -> validate citations
  -> stream to UI
  -> save chat history
  -> allow follow-up
```

