## Build Order

```txt
1. Backend search route
2. Search service
3. Scraper service
4. LLM service
5. Citation service
6. Basic frontend Home + ChatInput
7. ChatThread + SourcePanel
8. SSE streaming
9. Save chat history
10. Library
11. Settings
12. Usage limits
13. Billing/files/spaces/sharing
```

